<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - FolioPort" description="Privacy policy for FolioPort static portfolio generator">
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
    <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> / FolioPort
  </p>

  <h1>FolioPort Privacy Policy</h1>
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 0;">Static Portfolio Generator</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    FolioPort is a static portfolio generator that converts public GitHub data into a personal website. 
    It sources information from your public GitHub profile to create a stunning portfolio site.
  </p>

  <h2>Information Collected</h2>
  
  <h3>Data You Provide</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>GitHub username</li>
    <li>Custom content (bio, links, descriptions)</li>
    <li>Personalization settings</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Public GitHub Data</h3>
  <p>FolioPort reads only <strong>publicly available</strong> GitHub information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Public repositories</li>
    <li>Stars and forks</li>
    <li>Programming languages used</li>
    <li>Public contributions</li>
    <li>README files</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data FolioPort Never Accesses</h2>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <strong>FolioPort NEVER accesses:</strong>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Private repositories</li>
    <li>GitHub authentication tokens</li>
    <li>Email addresses</li>
    <li>Sensitive project information</li>
    <li>Private gists or notes</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Storage</h2>
  <p>
    The generated portfolio is a static website. <strong>No persistent data is stored on our servers.</strong>
  </p>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <p><strong>Generated Files:</strong> Stored temporarily during generation, then deleted</p>
    <p><strong>User Input:</strong> Not stored unless you explicitly save a project configuration</p>
    <p><strong>Analytics:</strong> None collected by FolioPort</p>
  </p>

  <h2>Hosting Your Portfolio</h2>
  <p>
    You own and host the generated portfolio. Hosting providers may have their own privacy policies:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>GitHub Pages</li>
    <li>Vercel</li>
    <li>Netlify</li>
    <li>Your own server</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Consult their privacy policies for information about how they handle your portfolio data.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    FolioPort reads data from GitHub's public API. 
    Refer to <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" target="_blank">GitHub's Privacy Policy</a> 
    for details about their data handling.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy inquiries, contact us at:<br />
    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dps.manit@gmail.com">dps.manit@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p><a href="/privacy">‚Üê Back to Master Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
